     }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.7em;\n            }\n\n            .property-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Aura Properties</h1>\n        <p>Discover your dream home with elegance and expertise.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"featured-properties\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-grid\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/1a3a7f/ffffff?text=Modern+Villa\" alt=\"Modern Villa\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Modern Villa with Ocean View</h3>\n                        <p>Luxurious 5-bedroom villa offering breathtaking panoramic ocean views and state-of-the-art amenities.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$2,500,000</div>\n                        <div class=\"details\">\n                            <span>5 Beds</span>\n                            <span>4 Baths</span>\n                            <span>5000 sqft</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/4d71b4/ffffff?text=Urban+Loft\" alt=\"Urban Loft\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Chic Urban Loft</h3>\n                        <p>Stylish 2-bedroom loft in the heart of the city, featuring industrial design and open-plan living.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$850,000</div>\n                        <div class=\"details\">\n                            <span>2 Beds</span>\n                            <span>2 Baths</span>\n                            <span>1500 sqft</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/1a3a7f/ffffff?text=Cozy+Cottage\" alt=\"Cozy Cottage\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Tranquil Lakeside Cottage</h3>\n                        <p>A charming 3-bedroom cottage nestled by a serene lake, perfect for a peaceful retreat.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$650,000</div>\n                        <div class=\"details\">\n                            <span>3 Beds</span>\n                            <span>2 Baths</span>\n                            <span>1800 sqft</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-grid\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Buying</h3>\n                        <p>Let us guide you through the process of finding and acquiring your perfect property.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Selling</h3>\n                        <p>Maximize your return with our expert marketing and negotiation strategies.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Consulting</h3>\n                        <p>Gain valuable insights and advice for your real estate investments.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-card\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <div class=\"property-info\">\n                    <p>Ready to find your next property or need expert advice? Get in touch with our team today!</p>\n                    <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@auraproperties.com\">info@auraproperties.com</a></p>\n                    <p>Phone: <a href=\"tel:+11234567890\">+1 (123) 456-7890</a></p>\n                    <p>Visit us at: 123 Blue Avenue, Metropolis</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Aura Properties. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p><a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic smooth scrolling for anchor links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}